{"id":236096,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-成都进京上访的访民多人被截访/","date":"2012-06-30T21:31:36Z","modified":"2012-06-30T21:31:36Z","title":"维权网 | 成都进京上访的访民多人被截访","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张银书报道）据成都在京上访的访民周成群在电话中称：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点</span><span>左右，她们一行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>人在路过府右街派出所附近时，有九人被府右街派出所扣留，只有吴铭仁一人逃脱。下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分左右，一行人被府右街派出所送往久敬庄黑监狱关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>被送往久敬庄关押的访民有周成群、曾少梅、李廷惠、李发清、刘廷芳、辜素芳、陈伦珍、陈新林和袁香蓉，其中金牛区的陈新林是昨天才与周成群等人碰面的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>分，他们九人从久敬庄被押上一辆中巴车，车牌为京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A4336</span><span>，打算连夜送回成都，押送他们的是一名自称叫做刘建的成都警官，警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">040371</span><span>，带领一群不明身份的人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据访民们说，这次被送回去，是否能安全回家或将面临处罚不得而知，大家希望社会各界关注他们的命运。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这些访民大都是因为房屋被非法拆迁，或司法不公的受害者，他们长期向各级政府上访反映诉求，但十多年过去了，问题一直得不到解决，因而才趁“七一”之机进京上访，试图引起有关部门的重视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道：“七一”将至，成都大批访民赴北京上访诉冤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_2391.htm\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_2391.htm</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4975522057304014106?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,17850,20534],"tags":[9085,16910,28519]}